---
description: Chain spec, provider, metrics, tracing, and secret handling
globs:
  - "bin/rundler/src/cli/**/*.rs"
  - "bin/rundler/chain_specs/**/*.toml"
  - "crates/provider/src/**/*.rs"
  - "crates/utils/src/log.rs"
---

- Preserve chain spec precedence: `CHAIN_*`, `--chain_spec`, `--network`, base, defaults.
- Keep JSON config loading compatible with local files and `s3://bucket/key`.
- Compose provider retry, consistency retry, metrics, and timeout layers deliberately.
- Add scoped metrics for new hot paths and keep logs structured.
- Never log private keys, mnemonics, auth headers, or raw signatures.

Full details: `.agents/skills/configuration-observability/`.

